#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.60"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.60:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.60:0.2"
msgid "6. Puññābhisandavagga"
msgstr "6. Overflowing Merit"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: gihisāmīcipaṭipadāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.60:0.3"
msgid "60. Gihisāmīcisutta"
msgstr "60. Lay Practice"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.65"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.60:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho "
"anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then the householder Anāthapiṇḍika went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat "
"down to one side. The Buddha said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.60:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Catūhi kho, gahapati, dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako gihisāmīcipaṭipadaṃ "
"paṭipanno hoti yasopaṭilābhiniṃ saggasaṃvattanikaṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Householder, when a noble disciple does four things they are practicing "
"appropriately for a layperson, which brings fame and leads to heaven."

msgctxt "an4.60:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.60:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, gahapati, ariyasāvako bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhito hoti cīvarena, "
"bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhito hoti piṇḍapātena, bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhito "
"hoti senāsanena, bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhito hoti "
"gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a noble disciple serves the mendicant Saṅgha with robes, alms-"
"food, lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick."

msgctxt "an4.60:2.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, gahapati, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako "
"gihisāmīcipaṭipadaṃ paṭipanno hoti yasopaṭilābhiniṃ saggasaṃvattanikanti."
msgstr ""
"When a noble disciple does these four things they are practicing "
"appropriately for a layperson, which brings fame and leads to heaven."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.60:3.1"
msgid "Gihisāmīcipaṭipadaṃ,"
msgstr "Those who are astute practice the way"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:3.2"
msgid "paṭipajjanti paṇḍitā;"
msgstr "that’s appropriate for laypeople."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:3.3"
msgid "Sammaggate sīlavante,"
msgstr "They provide those who are ethical"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:3.4"
msgid "cīvarena upaṭṭhitā."
msgstr "and on the right path with robes,"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.60:4.1"
msgid "Piṇḍapātasayanena,"
msgstr "alms-food, lodgings,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:4.2"
msgid "Gilānappaccayena ca;"
msgstr "and supplies for the sick."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:4.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ divā ca ratto ca,"
msgstr "Their merit always grows"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:4.4"
msgid "Sadā puññaṃ pavaḍḍhati;"
msgstr "by day and by night."

#. <br>
#. VAR: Saggañca kamatiṭṭhānaṃ → saggañca kamati ṭhānaṃ (pts1) | saggañca sappatiṭṭhānaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an4.60:4.5"
msgid "Saggañca kamatiṭṭhānaṃ,"
msgstr "They pass on to a place in heaven,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:4.6"
msgid "Kammaṃ katvāna bhaddakan”ti."
msgstr "having done excellent deeds.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.60:4.7"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.60:4.8"
msgid "Puññābhisandavaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.60:5.1"
msgid "Dve puññābhisandā dve ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:5.2"
msgid "saṃvāsā samajīvino;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:5.3"
msgid "Suppavāsā sudatto ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:5.4"
msgid "bhojanaṃ gihisāmicīti."
msgstr ""
